{"tid":1331422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉連毆「連儂牆」義工13拳 男子今提堂戴口罩到庭","createTime":"2019-07-19T02:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T02:45:52.000Z","uid":271284,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1495f6a62b3f5f7f27cb65f324ccbcc560568699","tid":1331422,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"轉左髮型，大家認能住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w28freD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw28freD.png&h=237fbcff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在逆權運動中，以和平手法表達市民心聲的「連儂牆」在各區遍地開花，但有人疑對此不滿，本月11日在九龍灣巴士站附近的「連儂牆」涉先後襲擊兩名看守的義工，包括連毆36歲義工13拳。涉行兇的黃姓男子事後被控兩項襲擊致造成實際身體傷害罪，案件今早於觀塘裁判法院提堂，未知他是否生病，戴著口罩抵庭。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190719/59839445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F59839445&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=986f19db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F59839445&h=c3d9ba4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190719/59839445</a>"},{"pid":"1ef5fc2d79fea74a6e5fa6921ed935667b6c5ff7","tid":1331422,"uid":54181,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81e396595fec1d90645d7c920d70cb71f9dbd1b8","tid":1331422,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"未知他是否生病，戴著口罩抵庭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f448412c9df91addea9df730fb65096160df36f","tid":1331422,"uid":124623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"戴口罩？？暴徒？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"